<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:30:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙只有一种可行的战后战略，但内塔尼亚胡还有其他计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-only-one-viable-postwar-strategy-for-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-plans/0000018b-b611-df42-a78f-bf53a5080000</link><description>真正的战斗正在耶路撒冷进行，而不是加沙。以色列主流和拜登政府认识到，唯一合理的行动方针是解散哈马斯并将加沙的管理权移交给国际部队和巴勒斯坦权力机构。内塔尼亚胡和弥赛亚右派不同意</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:10:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-only-one-viable-postwar-strategy-for-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-plans/0000018b-b611-df42-a78f-bf53a5080000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学宣布在以色列与哈马斯战争后打击反犹太主义的具体计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/harvard-announces-concrete-plan-to-fight-antisemitism/0000018b-b625-d3c1-a39b-bee5ce720000</link><description>此举是在犹太学生、校友和捐助者猛烈抨击这所常春藤盟校没有对以色列与哈马斯战争引发的反犹太主义行为做出更强有力的反应之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 23:59:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/harvard-announces-concrete-plan-to-fight-antisemitism/0000018b-b625-d3c1-a39b-bee5ce720000</guid></item><item><title>“我们正在慢慢死去。我已经两天没吃饭了，一直口渴”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-dying-slowly-i-havent-eaten-for-two-days-and-im-thirsty-all-the-time/0000018b-b5cc-d3c1-a39b-bfed66930000</link><description>一个月的连续轰炸造成加沙地带陷入粮食危机。父母为了给孩子吃饭而不吃饭；人们饮用受污染的水来充饥；其他人则在排队等待面包时被杀。联合国警告：加沙人已经突破极限</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 22:56:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-dying-slowly-i-havent-eaten-for-two-days-and-im-thirsty-all-the-time/0000018b-b5cc-d3c1-a39b-bfed66930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在损害其公民的抗议权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/israel-is-undermining-its-citizens-right-to-protest/0000018b-b5cd-dea2-a9bf-f5dffba40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 21:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/israel-is-undermining-its-citizens-right-to-protest/0000018b-b5cd-dea2-a9bf-f5dffba40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对尼尔奥兹基布兹的精心作战计划是什么样的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-hamas-meticulous-battle-plan-for-kibbutz-nir-oz-looked-like/0000018b-b4b7-dea2-a9bf-f4bf38970000</link><description>哈马斯在尼尔奥兹基布兹（其四分之一的居民被谋杀或绑架）留下的文件显示了该恐怖组织获取的高水平情报。以色列国防军在技术和物理障碍上投入了数十亿美元，却没有注意到</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 21:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-hamas-meticulous-battle-plan-for-kibbutz-nir-oz-looked-like/0000018b-b4b7-dea2-a9bf-f4bf38970000</guid></item><item><title>分而治之——以色列人和巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-divide-and-conquer-both-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018b-b5cd-df42-a78f-bdcfff7f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 21:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-divide-and-conquer-both-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018b-b5cd-df42-a78f-bdcfff7f0000</guid></item><item><title>我们现在需要在加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-need-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-now/0000018b-b5c2-d3c1-a39b-bfe3cee20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 21:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-need-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-now/0000018b-b5c2-d3c1-a39b-bfe3cee20000</guid></item><item><title>战争迷雾下，以色列执法部门让司法政变成为现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/under-the-fog-of-war-israeli-law-enforcement-make-judicial-coup-a-reality/0000018b-b5a2-df42-a78f-bde32f610000</link><description>前议员因抗议战争而被拘留，一名妇女因涂鸦而被认定为公共安全威胁，针对阿拉伯公民的指控层出不穷；以色列的执法机构正在为政府工作并反对民主</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 20:32:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/under-the-fog-of-war-israeli-law-enforcement-make-judicial-coup-a-reality/0000018b-b5a2-df42-a78f-bde32f610000</guid></item><item><title>加入反犹分子的犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/the-jews-who-join-the-jew-baiters/0000018b-b53b-dea2-a9bf-f5bfd72c0000</link><description>即使是在危险时刻无法支持其他犹太人的犹太人也不能与社区隔绝。相反，犹太人一直有更好的制裁：永远记住叛徒的行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 20:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/the-jews-who-join-the-jew-baiters/0000018b-b53b-dea2-a9bf-f5bfd72c0000</guid></item><item><title>被告知南迁的加沙人必须在以色列的轰炸和疾病之间做出选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/gazans-told-to-move-south-must-choose-between-israeli-bombardment-and-disease/0000018b-b550-df42-a78f-bd5359900000</link><description>随着逃离加沙地带北部的平民人数增加，有关以色列袭击南部“安全区”以及流离失所者营地的拥堵和卫生隐患的报道也随之增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:56:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/gazans-told-to-move-south-must-choose-between-israeli-bombardment-and-disease/0000018b-b550-df42-a78f-bd5359900000</guid></item><item><title>“我发现自己感到非常害怕”：随着加沙战争后反犹太主义的蔓延，美国的犹太人保持低调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-in-america-lie-low-as-antisemitism-spirals-in-wake-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b404-d3c1-a39b-bee5c5550000</link><description>犹太裔美国人有生以来第一次感到有必要隐藏自己的宗教和种族身份。一些人解释了原因，而另一些人则透露了为什么尽管一些城市普遍存在反以色列情绪，但他们拒绝掩饰自己的犹太身份</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-in-america-lie-low-as-antisemitism-spirals-in-wake-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b404-d3c1-a39b-bee5c5550000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯兰圣战组织发布了以色列男孩和老年妇女被绑架到加沙的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/islamic-jihad-releases-video-of-israeli-boy-and-elderly-woman-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018b-b57f-dedf-adab-f57f55630000</link><description>视频中的主角是 13 岁的亚吉尔·雅科夫 (Yagil Yaakov) 和 77 岁的汉娜·卡齐尔 (Hanna Katzir)，两人都来自尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz)。该恐怖组织表示，出于人道主义原因，他们准备释放人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:43:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/islamic-jihad-releases-video-of-israeli-boy-and-elderly-woman-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018b-b57f-dedf-adab-f57f55630000</guid></item><item><title>加沙一名士兵的感想：我们还会在这里看到多少次日出？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-soldiers-thoughts-in-gaza-how-many-more-sunrises-will-we-see-here/0000018b-b3ef-dedf-adab-f7ff52b50000</link><description>经过一个月的预备役服役后，这里没有英雄主义的故事，几乎没有阵雨，但有很多问题。我第一次回家几个小时，一切都感觉不一样了。甚至我的孩子们。也许我也是</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-soldiers-thoughts-in-gaza-how-many-more-sunrises-will-we-see-here/0000018b-b3ef-dedf-adab-f7ff52b50000</guid></item><item><title>整个以色列家庭被哈马斯关押：“三代人坐在地下”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/entire-israeli-families-held-by-hamas-three-generations-sitting-underground/0000018b-b3d3-dea2-a9bf-f3df988c0000</link><description>被关押在加沙的五个家庭的亲属向《国土报》讲述了他们生命中最糟糕的四个星期</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 18:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/entire-israeli-families-held-by-hamas-three-generations-sitting-underground/0000018b-b3d3-dea2-a9bf-f3df988c0000</guid></item><item><title>在战争中，以色列左派发现自己真正孤独</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-09/ty-article/.highlight/in-war-israeli-leftists-find-themselves-truly-alone/0000018b-b52b-d3c1-a39b-bfeb9d690000</link><description>打击对阿拉伯人、巴勒斯坦人和其他少数民族的迫害是一场艰苦的战斗。当我们同时必须提醒我们所谓的盟友我们也被允许存在时，这就变得更加困难</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 18:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-09/ty-article/.highlight/in-war-israeli-leftists-find-themselves-truly-alone/0000018b-b52b-d3c1-a39b-bfeb9d690000</guid></item><item><title>你会吃一块含有假脂肪的饼干来拯救地球吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-09/ty-article/would-you-eat-a-cookie-with-fake-fat-to-save-the-planet/0000018b-b4a0-dedf-adab-f5b0fc850000</link><description>您很可能不知道馅饼皮从哪里来并且不在乎，那么您会改用人造油来拯救地球吗？</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 17:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-09/ty-article/would-you-eat-a-cookie-with-fake-fat-to-save-the-planet/0000018b-b4a0-dedf-adab-f5b0fc850000</guid></item><item><title>非法接管 30 年后，高等法院命令定居者离开巴勒斯坦土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/30-years-after-illegal-takeover-high-court-orders-settlers-out-of-palestinian-land/0000018b-b4db-dea2-a9bf-f4dfdc120000</link><description>以色列定居者一直在这片土地上种植椰枣，法院裁定这片土地是非法移交给他们的。法院表示，这种种植行为“不仅违反了国际法和政府宣布的政策，甚至违反了哈拉克法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/30-years-after-illegal-takeover-high-court-orders-settlers-out-of-palestinian-land/0000018b-b4db-dea2-a9bf-f4dfdc120000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德和中央情报局局长会见卡塔尔总理讨论人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-cia-chiefs-meet-with-qatari-pm-to-discuss-hostage-deal/0000018b-b4af-dea2-a9bf-f4bf183a0000</link><description>据报道，会谈包括关于暂停加沙战斗和允许向飞地进口人道主义燃料的讨论，以换取释放 10 至 15 名以色列人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-cia-chiefs-meet-with-qatari-pm-to-discuss-hostage-deal/0000018b-b4af-dea2-a9bf-f4bf183a0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，四分之三的美国犹太人因以色列与哈马斯的战争而担心自己的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-u-s-jews-fear-for-their-safety-because-of-israel-hamas-war-poll-shows/0000018b-b4e1-df42-a78f-bde312120000</link><description>在为北美犹太联合会进行的一项民意调查中，三分之二的犹太裔美国人将他们社区的气氛描述为紧张、不舒服或可怕</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-u-s-jews-fear-for-their-safety-because-of-israel-hamas-war-poll-shows/0000018b-b4e1-df42-a78f-bde312120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席：巴勒斯坦权力机构每天都在努力阻止支持哈马斯的示威活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-palestinian-authority-works-daily-to-prevent-demonstrations-in-support-of-hamas/0000018b-b496-dea2-a9bf-f49e87590000</link><description>以色列国防军参谋长赫茨尔·哈勒维回应了一名极右翼议员，后者在没有证据的情况下声称巴勒斯坦权力机构可能会加入战斗，以此作为与哈马斯团结的标志</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-palestinian-authority-works-daily-to-prevent-demonstrations-in-support-of-hamas/0000018b-b496-dea2-a9bf-f49e87590000</guid></item></channel></rss>